Class FileHandlerModel

java.lang.Object
  com.nokia.midp.examples.JSR75.FileHandler.FileHandlerModel
public class FileHandlerModel
extends java.lang.Object

This class is for user command handling. All commands targeted on specific volume are added to a vector. With this the Action menu is contructed.
